{"tid":1911000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥及陳帆視察青衣長康邨    未有上樓就離開","createTime":"2020-03-05T05:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T09:30:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d30f8b1d551ed5deab5347c347c9e90dd6cf881","tid":1911000,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ySW0muM7ZusmYepZ78YXEw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/CE-VISIT-200304-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FySW0muM7ZusmYepZ78YXEw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FCE-VISIT-200304-12.jpg&h=353abb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥及運輸及房屋局局長陳帆到青衣長康邨視察，全程逗留不足半小時，未有上樓就離開。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥的座駕早上11時前到達青衣長康邨，她先到社會福利署的辦事處逗留約20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥之後到屋邨外視察大廈喉管，有房署職員在旁講解。<br />\n<br />\n康美樓兩個不同樓層的07室單位，上月初先後有人確診新型冠狀病毒，同座的07室住戶一度要送往檢疫中心，讓政府消毒及檢查渠管。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥視察後上車離開，全程不足半小時。有住客趕來，官員已離開。<br />\n<br />\n今次視察未有通知傳媒採訪。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥到康美樓巡視的消息，早一晚已經在網上流傳，而她到達前約一小時，已經有大批警員及政府職員到場準備。"},{"pid":"3310f58173755bca8c646e8ac6ff275416fb1cb3","tid":1911000,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"浪費公帑&amp;狗力做show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceac609520184aae662916625cd19be123f8d51","tid":1911000,"uid":339053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭月娥之後到屋邨外視察大廈喉管，有房署職員在旁講解。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n啲渠喺屋裡面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 柒婆有透視眼呀"},{"pid":"35bccc8cb0b30a468303bcb3372ad2aab27cb32f","tid":1911000,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"做特首辦報告一定要有呢d相"}]}